# Core boundary

- **src/core** must NEVER import from:
  - **src/ui**
  - **app/** (pages, layout)
  - **components/** (React UI)
- Core may import from: **lib/** (Supabase, server utils), **src/core** (self), **src/design** (tokens only if needed for type), **src/core/types**.
- All `fetch('/api/...')` from UI must go through **src/core/api/** wrappers. No direct fetch in app or components for app APIs.
